          <tr><td>Control board (non-HMI)</td><td>$600–$1,000</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prodigy HMI board</td><td>$650–$1,100</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Most Champion door-machine calls land $350–$700 parts-and-labor; 44-Series and 66-Series rack conveyor jobs
        run $550–$1,100. Full cross-brand pricing in our <a href="/price-list/commercial-dishwasher-repair-cost/">commercial
        dishwasher repair pricing guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related Champion and Ali Group family pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/cma-dishmachines-repair/">CMA Dishmachines repair Los Angeles</a>, Ali Group sister brand, value tier</li>
        <li><a href="/brands/kolpak-walk-in-repair/">Kolpak walk-in cooler repair Los Angeles</a>, Ali Group family, walk-in sibling</li>
